column5: Ventured out with a Buddy on Sunday.....was hoping to put him on is first Whities .  Poor man's Lobster had other ideas          After hooking into a few of them , I says to him ............'' Apparently '' they taste like cod / lobster .   Oh yeah...lets see                          I spent most of the day shaking off these Pesty buggers        Heading back again on Saturday...........Hopefully the Whitefish will be in the Mood to Play .
'Tis no whitie...  It's hard to convince yourself to keep them isn't it?
That's an interesting looking spoon.  Whities for ling.  Fun either way dood!  Some nice fish.
Ling it up!  At least it's some action....I definitely want to target them after all I've read about their fine table fare qualities
Don't forget the livers are a delicacy!
Nice going.  That is a laker in the last picture, right?
We unfortunately, get into ling as well once in awhile.  I tried them once ... ONCE.  My black lab hated me for a week when I gave it to her.
The ling are biting furiously on Nipissing. Here is the stomach content of one from last night.
Ling galore    The one in the pic before last, looks like it had some shoulders to it   did you keep any for the pan??
